2. **Full Neon: The Maximum Impact Manicure** — solid neon sets, the most searched core looks (hot pink, neon orange, electric yellow, lime green, neon coral)
3. **Neon French Tips: Bold Without the Commitment** — the entry point into neon; coloured tips over nude base; wavy neon tips; colour swaps across each finger
