5. **Neon Ombre and Gradient Nails** — single-colour fades from deep to light; sunset neon blends (pink to orange, yellow to green); the "glow from within" effect
6. **Neon Swirl and Abstract Designs** — the retro-psychedelic neon trend; squiggle lines, fluid curves, abstract painterly neon art over nude bases; the 2026 squoval neon swirl surge
7. **Skittle Nails: Every Finger a Different Neon** — the mix-and-match multi-colour set; how to make it feel cohesive vs chaotic; warm family vs cool family combos
8. **Which Neon Colour Suits Your Skin Tone** — the practical guide that competitors skip; fair, medium, olive, dark skin tone-specific shade direction; the universal flattering formats for each
9. **Neon Nails on Short Nails** — proof this trend works on shorter lengths; the best designs for shorter canvases (French tips, aura, single-shade solids)
10. **How to Make Your Neon Manicure Actually Last** — white base coat truth; why neon fades faster and how to slow it; gel vs regular for neon; UV exposure and topcoat reapplication
