**Structure Reasoning:** Moves from boldest to most wearable (max impact → French tip → aura → ombre), then layers in practical decision guides (skin tone, short nails, longevity). This mirrors both the inspirational browser (start at top, save what resonates) and the decision-maker (scroll to the guidance sections once they've found a look they love). The skin tone and short nail sections address the two biggest pain points that are currently a SERP gap — giving this post a clear advantage over pure gallery pages.

